      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks for catching this! Originally, I\u0027d kept GL_WAIT_FAILED with the EGL_CONDITION_SATISFIED_KHR group since I wasn\u0027t sure if host GPU drivers would really support the command. But, if this command fails, we don\u0027t fail dangerously anyway. Done",
